"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"12月10日消息，MicroStrategy CEO Michael Saylor（迈克尔塞勒）在接受采访时谈到了最近的国会听证会，并认为讨论的最终赢家是比特币。他认为刺激驱动的通胀环境对比特币有利，Saylor称黄金为死石，人们能做的最好的事情就是卖出价值10万亿美元的黄金并购买比特币。12月9日，Saylor发推称，以大约8240万美元现金买入1434枚比特币。\",\"timestamp\":1639114196,\"title\":\"MicroStrategy CEO：卖掉黄金并购买比特币是更好的选择\"},\"digest\":\"LAXuQ8lco-rrfJtgNCS-mcTKQ2PbRHFVqxlFgmEs5iQ\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x2d5a663eE740f368119A277a101ac49d40B03A1f\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"V9mFwKL2WdeEppcxc2RHWMliLRh8vilhn0PqPLpS2LA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"no6eMxqHJiZVPIjDG0c6bo8QhPeyQ9SoCeFSCt4Sfls\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"QqzjJYuTsU4pyWXQVJwsS2MiDq6w7wTIi1MsB40OaBcio-JuetIhHqKdpzgZbFZmb-bJI4lYtiKcl5s5635GoA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x840cca62f2ef9568176a0b68ebcda7461ac5ea5de1229b782660c2bcc761c5c514abca410fe0813fd0e56960c915cd740e314577b2743c275a9f1533b701b56c1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"V9mFwKL2WdeEppcxc2RHWMliLRh8vilhn0PqPLpS2LA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"no6eMxqHJiZVPIjDG0c6bo8QhPeyQ9SoCeFSCt4Sfls\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"LAXuQ8lco-rrfJtgNCS-mcTKQ2PbRHFVqxlFgmEs5iQ\"}"